# Revision history for App-Balance

0.02    2026-05-09
        Add Docker support: multi-stage Dockerfile, docker-compose.yml, and
        docker/entrypoint.sh. Requires rsync in the container for the apply
        command.

0.01    2026-04-30
        Initial CPAN release.
        Rebalances media folders across multiple storage mounts while
        keeping Sonarr and Plex synchronized. Includes Mojolicious web UI,
        async job runner, and CLI tools for plan/apply/reconcile workflows.
